      "span_text": "In fact, it has been proposed by [CITATION_1] that metformin inhibits the proliferation of DU 145, PC-3 and LNCaP cancer cells (prostate cancer cells), decreasing cell viability, as a consequence of blocking cell cycle in G 0 /G 1 and decreasing the levels of cyclin D1."
